Sentencas: Quantitative microstructural interpretations were carried out without human involvement through an integrated combination of deep learning and focused ion beam-scanning electron microscopy (FIB-SEM) analytics on Ni/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 (Ni/YSZ) cermets.
Titulo: Deep learning-assisted microstructural analysis of Ni/YSZ anode composites for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Ni/YSZ/pore composites were analyzed for the automated extraction of microstructural parameters to prevent the subjective analysis problems and unavoidable artifacts frequently encountered in lengthy image processing tasks and eliminate biased evaluations.
Titulo: Deep learning-assisted microstructural analysis of Ni/YSZ anode composites for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Considering the high volume of image data and future expectations for electron microscopy usage, FIB-SEM was efficiently combined with semantic segmentation.
Titulo: Deep learning-assisted microstructural analysis of Ni/YSZ anode composites for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Traditional image processing analysis tools are combined with phase separation predictions by semantic segmentation algorithms, leading to a quantitative evaluation of microstructural parameters.
Titulo: Deep learning-assisted microstructural analysis of Ni/YSZ anode composites for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The combined strategy enables one to significantly enhance poor image quality originating from artifacts in electron microscopy, including charging effects, curtain effects, out-of-focus problems, and unclear phase boundaries encountered in searching for high-efficiency solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Deep learning-assisted microstructural analysis of Ni/YSZ anode composites for solid oxide fuel cells
